{"Id":609922,"Title":"梁国桢寄曹溪露茶兼订住山之约答之","Dynasty":"明","Author":"李之世","Context":"曹溪老僧斲石骨。种得芽茶细似发。白露才过三两日，青布裹头笼焙出。嗅香果足醒心魂。郑重封函远记存。我曾一饮曹溪水。中泠惠山只如此。城中止数蟹眼潭。三十铜钱买一墰。我对佳茶想佳水，今年定住曹溪庵。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"0c13be7e000bb0ba60c62ff615ff977b","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":7236238,"Sentence":"曹溪老僧斲石骨。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"cáo xī lǎo sēng zhuó dàn gū ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7236239,"Sentence":"种得芽茶细似发。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"chóng dé yá chá xì shì fā ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7236240,"Sentence":"白露才过三两日，青布裹头笼焙出。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"bái lòu cái guō sān liǎng rì ，qīng bù guǒ tóu lóng bèi chū ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7236241,"Sentence":"嗅香果足醒心魂。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xìu xiāng guǒ zú xing xīn hún ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7236242,"Sentence":"郑重封函远记存。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zhèng chóng fēng hán yuǎn jì cún ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7236243,"Sentence":"我曾一饮曹溪水。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wǒ céng yī yin cáo xī shui ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7236244,"Sentence":"中泠惠山只如此。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zhōng lǐng huì shān zhī rú ci ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7236245,"Sentence":"城中止数蟹眼潭。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"chéng zhōng zhi shǔ xiè yǎn tán ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7236246,"Sentence":"三十铜钱买一墰。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"sān shǐ tóng qián mǎi yī tán ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":8,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7236247,"Sentence":"我对佳茶想佳水，今年定住曹溪庵。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wǒ duì jiā